      "created_at": "2023-04-01T11:58:39.897Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi,</p>\n<p>I made a 8 week plan with coach Jack and I set my long outdoor rides in the weekend.<br>\nthe problem is that sometimes the weather is just very bad, so I was wondering if I can convert a long outdoor ride to multiple shorter indoor rides on the day itself?</p>\n<p>I only get the option to copy the training as it is made by coach Jack.</p>\n<p>Any idea how/if this is possible?</p>\n<p>Thanks in advance,<br>\nTony</p>",
